Package: soilgraph
Title: Soil Profile Visualization from Field Descriptions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
        given = "Nicolás",
        family = "Riveras-Muñoz",
        email = "contact@nriveras.com",
        role = c("aut", "cre")
    ))
Description: Parse free-text soil field descriptions into structured data,
    export profiles to a standardised JSON schema, and render publication-ready
    visualisations with irregular coarse-fragment and horizon-boundary engines
    powered by 'ggplot2'. Follows Soil Taxonomy (USDA) vocabulary for texture,
    moisture, colour, boundary grade and shape, and coarse fragment properties.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://nriveras.github.io/soilgraph
BugReports: https://github.com/nriveras/soilgraph/-/issues
